        {
            "title": "次季開局高收 滬指收升56點 深指漲1.7% 創新藥股升勢勁",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍市況午後進一步反彈，繼續支持內地A股回升，滬深兩市股指午後均曾升越早市高位；創新藥板塊受捧，藥明康德(02359)A股(603259.SH)漲逾半成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02359Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"藥明康德官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02359Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">藥明康德官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早高開47點後便在高位徘徊，初段出現的全日低位3929點時仍升38點0.98%，其後穩步向上，午後最高衝上3955點，將升幅擴大至64點或1.65%，其後進入整固，但升幅一直超過1%；滬指最後收報3948點，升56點或1.46%，成交8972.78億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指今早在顯著高開後升幅收窄，開市數分鐘內升幅由逾250點一度縮減至125點或0.93%，低見13606點，隨即開始小半日在13700點之下橫行的階段，午後重新發力，最高見13740點，升262點或1.95%，繼而重現整固；深指收報13706點，升228點或1.7%，成交1.115萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也升76點或1.71%，以4526點收市；創業板指數漲62點或1.96%，報3247點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創新藥板塊愈升愈有，藥明康德A股再成百元股，收報103.81元，升5.82%；榮昌生物(09995)A股(688331.SH)升11.83%，報144元；君實生物(01877)A股(688180.SH)也升10.25%，報38.4元；凱萊英(06821)A股(002821.SZ)則在早市升約10%後封板。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">康龍化成(03759)A股(300759.SZ)也升8.58%，報30.38元；昭衍新藥(06127)A股(603127.SH)漲8.07%，報36.96元。百濟神州(06160)A股(688235.SH)則升6.98%，報249.9元；諾誠健華(09969)A股(688428.SH)也漲6.7%，報28.83元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：榮昌生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250626_FI_source-web_09995-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：榮昌生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250626_FI_source-web_09995-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：榮昌生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">芯片及半導體相關股午後維持強勢，今早已重越千元關口的寒武紀(688256.SH)，收漲6.96%，報1051.4元，成交104.11億元。華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)升幅擴大至7.6%，報113.95元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)則升2.42%，報96.33元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">油價期油價格在內地股市收市前失守每桶100美元水平，油股進一步受壓。中國海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)跌3.4%，報38.64元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)亦倒跌，收報12.07元，跌0.98%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15823522-%e6%ac%a1%e5%ad%a3%e9%96%8b%e5%b1%80%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%8756%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b21-7-%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e8%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e5%8b%a2%e5%8b%81",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 15:14:17",
