            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "嵐圖上月交付新車按年增50.15 今年累計升30.2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">嵐圖(07489)公布，於今年3月份交付新車1.5萬輛，按年升50.1%；今年累計交付3.39萬輛，較去年同期增加30.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：嵐圖官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260401_FI_source-web_07489.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：嵐圖官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260401_FI_source-web_07489.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：嵐圖官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司表示，嵐圖夢想家於上月10日迎來第20萬輛下線，冠軍版車型同步推出；在3月17<br/>  日，嵐圖泰山Ultra正式量產交付，嵐圖泰山黑武士同步上市；於3月19日，庭院級大五座SUV泰山X8正式亮相，計劃於今年第2季上市。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15822604-%e5%b5%90%e5%9c%96%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e4%ba%a4%e4%bb%98%e6%96%b0%e8%bb%8a%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e50-15-%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e5%8d%8730-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/07489-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 12:15:00",
